channel.title: The hell is wrong with the interwebs?
channel.description:
Well, it either my Internet or the hosters connection. I've been trying to get on sites, and they load for 2-3 minute and then stop altogether, giving me a blank page. When I ask others if it works, it loads easily with no problem.
What could be the problem?
